dataset_description.json.HowToAcknowledge: C. Baldassano, D.M. Beck, L. Fei-Fei. Human–Object Interactions Are More than the Sum of Their Parts. Cerebral Cortex, 2016. doi: 10.1093/cercor/bhw077

README: This dataset corresponds to Experiment 2 in "Human–Object Interactions Are More than the Sum of Their Parts" (2016) by Baldassano, Beck, and Fei-Fei (10.1093/cercor/bhw077). Each of the 12 subjects has 14 functional runs, as well as an anatomical scan that has been skull-stripped using AFNI's 3dSkullStrip. The stimulus images are available at https://figshare.com/articles/Human-Object_Stimuli_Experiment_2/5213350.
